        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.9999999046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "やったー、逆転勝利！\n楽しかったー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes~! A come-from-behind victory!\nThat was fun~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9999999046,
      "endTime": 15.7940136909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9999999046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "高校でもいろんな部活のヘルプで誘われて\n中学の時と同じように楽しくやってたんだけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In high school‚ I was invited to help out with various clubs too‚\nand I was having fun just like in middle school――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9999999046,
      "endTime": 23.8465306282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0333332379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho001.m4a",
      "text": "早坂さん、って言ったかしら？\n突然ごめんなさいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hayasaka-san‚ was it?\nSorry to bother you so suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0333332379,
      "endTime": 29.453332885000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho002.m4a",
      "text": "私、チアリーディング部の部長をやっているの\n早坂さん、チアに興味はない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm the captain of the cheerleading club.\nHayasaka-san‚ are you interested in cheerleading?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6666661898,
      "endTime": 37.1666655222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.3666654269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "チアって……ポンポンを持って試合の時に踊る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheerleading… is that where you dance with pom-poms during games?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666654269,
      "endTime": 41.7485250155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9333320935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho003.m4a",
      "text": "そのイメージで合ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9333320935,
      "endTime": 43.9799978097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの練習試合を見たんだけど、あなたは運動神経が\n素晴らしいだけじゃなくて、とても華があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw your practice match earlier‚ and not only are you incredibly athletic‚\nbut you also have a really captivating presence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3333361625,
      "endTime": 52.540003395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.7333366711
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　えへへ、そんなそんな、照れるなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Ehehe‚ you're making me blush~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333366711,
      "endTime": 58.2895951588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho005.m4a",
      "text": "この後体育館でチア部の練習があるの\n良かったら覗いてみない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have cheer club practice at the gym later‚\nwould you like to come watch?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5000033378,
      "endTime": 63.626669693000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.8333364169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ sure~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8333364169,
      "endTime": 65.6384384553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.8333364169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "最初はただ見学するだけのつもりだったんだけど\nチア部のパフォーマンスがすっごくかっこ良くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just planning on watching at first‚\nbut the cheer club's performance was so cool‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8333364169,
      "endTime": 74.6005242983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "何よりみんなとっても楽しそうで……\n入部してみることにしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and everyone looked like they were having so much fun…\nSo I decided to join.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8000030835,
      "endTime": 82.0446742375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――芽衣がチア部に加入してしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Mei joined the cheerleading club.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9666661899,
      "endTime": 85.1999980291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.1999980291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho006.m4a",
      "text": "地区予選の選抜メンバー、最後の一人は……\n早坂芽衣さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final member of the regional qualifiers selection team is…\nMei Hayasaka!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666636467,
      "endTime": 92.3733324528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5666656812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "はーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5666656812,
      "endTime": 94.2114729484,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1833.3333333999917,
          "startTime": 94.3999990146
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.3999990146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "部員",
      "speakerNameEn": "Member",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-buin001.m4a",
      "text": "早坂さんが選抜メンバー入り……？\nついこの間入ったばかりなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hayasaka made the selection team…?\nShe just joined…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3999990146,
      "endTime": 100.8133303324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.99999698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho007.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、静かに。一年生が選ばれたことに\n不満を覚える人がいるかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ quiet down. I understand that some of you\nmight have objections to a first-year being chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.99999698,
      "endTime": 107.4799968083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho008.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、早坂さんの動きのキレや華やかさを見れば\n当然のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you look at Hayasaka's sharp movements and her vibrant aura‚\nit's only natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666636467,
      "endTime": 113.2999947548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.4999949455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……そんなに褒めてもらえるなんて嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… It makes me happy to be praised so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4999949455,
      "endTime": 118.66475677490001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8666616122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho009.m4a",
      "text": "今回の選び方に何か意見があれば私に言って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any opinions about how the selection was made‚ please speak to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666616122,
      "endTime": 123.6866570632,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.661580399995,
          "startTime": 123.9333231926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9333231926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_02-bucho010.m4a",
      "text": "さあ！　気持ちを切り替えて！\n練習を始めます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now! Let's reset our minds!\nWe're starting practice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.9333231926,
      "endTime": 127.6799841881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
